  <LegalSection title="Independence statement"><p>NozzleNote by BMR is an independent product and is not affiliated with, endorsed by, sponsored by, certified by, reviewed by, or officially connected to Bambu Lab, Creality, Anycubic, Prusa, or any other 3D printer manufacturer. Manufacturer and product names may be referenced only to help users describe their own equipment or future compatibility context.</p></LegalSection>
  <LegalSection title="Compatibility context"><p>Future compatibility language should be narrow and model-specific, such as compatible with selected Bambu Lab printer models only after coverage is defined. Broad compatibility claims should not be used.</p></LegalSection>
  <LegalSection title="Trademarks and names"><p>Manufacturer names, printer family names, and product names belong to their respective owners. References do not imply endorsement, review, approval, certification, sponsorship, or support.</p></LegalSection>
  <LegalSection title="Printer data may change"><p>Printer specifications, parts, firmware, maintenance guidance, and manufacturer documentation may change. Users should consult the relevant manufacturer documentation and qualified help where appropriate.</p></LegalSection>
  <LegalSection title="Not a service portal"><p>NozzleNote is being developed for maintenance tracking and recordkeeping. It is not a manufacturer service portal, warranty channel, repair service, safety system, or remote printer controller.</p></LegalSection>
</LegalLayout>
